      "Uid": null,
      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "Wolfgang.Etl.TestKit.FaultyExtractor<T>",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Wolfgang.Etl.TestKit.FaultyExtractor-1.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">An in-memory extractor for testing error-handling paths. It yields items from an\n<xref href=\"System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> like a normal extractor, but can be configured to inject\ndeterministic faults — throwing at a given item, throwing after completion, or\nduplicating an item — so consumers can exercise mid-stream failure, finalization\nfailure, and de-duplication logic without hand-rolling broken fakes.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "ManagedReference",
      "source_relative_path": "api/Wolfgang.Etl.TestKit.FaultyLoader-1.yml",
      "output": {
        ".html": {
          "relative_path": "api/Wolfgang.Etl.TestKit.FaultyLoader-1.html"
        }
      },
      "version": "",
      "Uid": null,
      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "Wolfgang.Etl.TestKit.FaultyLoader<T>",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Wolfgang.Etl.TestKit.FaultyLoader-1.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">An in-memory loader for testing error-handling paths. It consumes the source stream\nlike a normal loader, but can be configured to inject deterministic faults — throwing\nat a given item, throwing after completion, or duplicating an item — so consumers can\nexercise mid-stream failure, finalization failure, and idempotency logic without\nhand-rolling broken fakes.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "ManagedReference",
      "source_relative_path": "api/Wolfgang.Etl.TestKit.FaultyTransformer-1.yml",
      "output": {
        ".html": {
          "relative_path": "api/Wolfgang.Etl.TestKit.FaultyTransformer-1.html"
        }
      },
      "version": "",
      "Uid": null,
      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "Wolfgang.Etl.TestKit.FaultyTransformer<T>",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Wolfgang.Etl.TestKit.FaultyTransformer-1.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">A pass-through transformer for testing error-handling paths. It returns each item\nunchanged like a normal transformer, but can be configured to inject deterministic\nfaults — throwing at a given item, throwing after completion, or duplicating an item —\nso consumers can exercise mid-stream failure, finalization failure, and de-duplication\nlogic without hand-rolling broken fakes.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "ManagedReference",
      "source_relative_path": "api/Wolfgang.Etl.TestKit.TestExtractor-1.yml",
      "output": {
        ".html": {
          "relative_path": "api/Wolfgang.Etl.TestKit.TestExtractor-1.html"
        }
      },
      "version": "",
      "Uid": null,
      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "Wolfgang.Etl.TestKit.TestExtractor<T>",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Wolfgang.Etl.TestKit.TestExtractor-1.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">An in-memory extractor for use in tests, examples, and benchmarks.\nYields items from an <xref href=\"System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>, an\n<xref href=\"System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerator%601\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>, or a factory delegate, depending on which\nconstructor is used.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "ManagedReference",
      "source_relative_path": "api/Wolfgang.Etl.TestKit.TestLoader-1.yml",
      "output": {
        ".html": {
          "relative_path": "api/Wolfgang.Etl.TestKit.TestLoader-1.html"
        }
      },
      "version": "",
      "Uid": null,
      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "Wolfgang.Etl.TestKit.TestLoader<T>",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Wolfgang.Etl.TestKit.TestLoader-1.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">A simple in-memory loader for use in tests, examples, and benchmarks.\nIterates all items from the source stream and, when constructed with\n<code>collectItems: true</code>, makes them available via <xref href=\"Wolfgang.Etl.TestKit.TestLoader%601.GetCollectedItems\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>\nafter the load completes.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "ManagedReference",
      "source_relative_path": "api/Wolfgang.Etl.TestKit.TestTransformer-1.yml",
      "output": {
        ".html": {
          "relative_path": "api/Wolfgang.Etl.TestKit.TestTransformer-1.html"
        }
      },
      "version": "",
      "Uid": null,
      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "Wolfgang.Etl.TestKit.TestTransformer<T>",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Wolfgang.Etl.TestKit.TestTransformer-1.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">A pass-through transformer for use in tests, examples, and benchmarks.\nReturns each item unchanged, with no transformation applied.</p>\n"
